THE DECENTRALISED ART GALLERY  

 
 

Jan 2014 Founding team (DXMarkets) assembled. 

Nov 2014 First prototype of trading platform built. 

Apr 2015 First version (MVP) of trading platform released. 

Aug 2015 Friends & family funding round closed. 

Oct 2015 DXMarkets founding team selected to join Fintech Fusion acceleration programme in Geneva. 

Jan 2016 DXMarkets founding team coins the name Maecenas 

Feb 2016 Team starts validating product-market fit and reaching out to art market participants. 

May 2016 Business model fully validated and public website is released. 

Jun 2016 Maecenas starts buidling a blockchain-enabled platform for issuance of art assets. 

Jul 2016 Operational model & legal frameword for blockchain co-ownership of art. 

Sep 2016 Maecenas graduates from Fintech Fusion. 

Nov 2016 First prototype of Maecenas is completed. 

Feb 2017 Investment from Polytech Ventures is secured. 

Apr 2017 Maecenas MVP is completed. 

May 2017 30+ artworks in pipeline worth over $100 M. 

Jul 2017 Maecenas crowdsale is announced. 



 
